name: Euphoria
public_notice: Euphoria had ceased operation, kindly refer to this post for more information.

description.en: Euphoria is a new DeFi 2.0 primitive on Harmony that is largely inspired by OlympusDAO and Wonderland. The project was launched by VenomDAO - creators of Harmony's longest running DEX ViperSwap.
